wo prostrations before and after noon prayer, two prostrations after sunset prayer, two prostrations after evening prayer, and two prostrations after Friday prayer. As for sunset and evening prayer, they were in his house. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36828,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/08\/22\/waqt-salawat-al-khams\/","url_meta":{"origin":25400,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Timings of the five prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 22, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen you perform the dawn prayer, its time is until the first rising of the sun. Then, when you perform noon prayer, its time is until the presence of afternoon. When you perform the afternoon\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13043,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/23\/twelve-sunan-voluntary-prayers\/","url_meta":{"origin":25400,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Twelve voluntary Sunan prayers rewarded","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Habibah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever performs twelve cycles of prayer in each day and night, a house will be built for them in Paradise.\" Umm Habibah said, \"I have never abandoned them since I heard it from the Messenger of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12956,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/two-before-maghrib\/","url_meta":{"origin":25400,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Two raka&#8217;at of recommended prayer before Maghrib","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: When the caller to prayer announced the prayer, people among the companions of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would stand and proceed to the pillars of the mosque until the Prophet came out to them. Thus, they would pray two cycles before sunset\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33619,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/24\/sunan-maghrib-if-you-wish\/","url_meta":{"origin":25400,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Recommended two raka&#8217;at before Maghrib","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Muzanni reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPray before the sunset prayer.\u201d The Prophet said on the third time, \u201cFor whomever wishes,\u201d as he disliked for people to consider it an obligatory tradition. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1183 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25415,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/13\/salat-shortened-two-rakaat-travel\/","url_meta":{"origin":25400,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Prayer shortened to two cycles during travel","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 13, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: I accompanied the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and during travel he would not add more to his prayer than two cycles. Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman did likewise, may Allah be pleased with them. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1051, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 689 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25400","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=25400"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2